summary: A new weapon pack, featuring craftable Mammoth-Tusk Weapons! Enjoy :D
descriptionHtml:
-----------------------------
v1.05 Better Balanced- --> theyre not enchanted. a bit better than daedric weapons.
-----------------------------
To get them:
1.Get mammoth tusks.
2.Craft Ivory Ingots at the smelter
3. Craft the weapons at every forge
4. enjoy :)


If u like this mood, leave a thumbsup plz :D
author: CSG13
